Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:49.98,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:58.89,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以最初的一步选择未知的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:02.81,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就以属于自己的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:09.06,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以最后的一步决定世界的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:13.04,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯一的赢家非我莫属
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:15.57,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已经亲眼见证了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:22.66,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁都无从预知的最佳答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:27.58,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是在棋盘上操纵一切的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:30.20,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}掀起思考的斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.74,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连错误也是伪装的假象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:35.24,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直至将死之前都在精心布局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:37.62,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是争抢王位的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:40.21,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遵从想法与欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:42.72,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一次机会 在劫难逃的坏棋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.77,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最后机会 势必要击溃劲敌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.76,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:50.70,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仅凭那种路数根本就无法追及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.84,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:58.24,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}将完全胜利紧握在手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:06.06,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有人都已望尘莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.75,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.76,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}そんな手じゃもう追いつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:49.98,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:58.89,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最初の一手で選ぶ 未知なるfuture
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:02.81,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その有り様 this way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:09.06,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後の一手で決める 世界のanswer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:13.04,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一人のwinner it's me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:15.57,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}この目は見据えた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:22.66,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰も未だ見通せぬ最適解を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:27.58,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全ては盤上支配するgame
