Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:37.62,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kingを奪い合うgame
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:40.21,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}思想と欲望
