Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.77,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Last chance 必ず仕留める
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.76,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:50.70,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}そんな手じゃもう追いつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.84,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
